Sigstr, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 3:40 PM ET
Software

Company Overview of Sigstr, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Sigstr, Inc. develops a cloud-based email signature marketing application. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is based in Indianapolis, Indiana.


55 Monument Circle14th FloorIndianapolis, IN 46204United StatesFounded in 2015



Phone: 317-714-7001

www.sigstr.com







Key Executives for Sigstr, Inc.


Sigstr, Inc. does not have any Key Executives recorded. 



Sigstr, Inc. Key Developments

Sigstr Launches New Account-Based Marketing Functionality
May 16 17
Sigstr announced the launch of its new Account-Based Marketing (ABM) functionality. For the first time, marketers can tap into employee emails to deliver 1:1 targeted content to specific accounts, industries and regions. Using Sigstr Campaigns, the new ABM functionality allows customers to assign an email signature campaign to individual recipients. When users email recipients associated with an ABM campaign, the Sigstr platform dynamically serves personalized content. The ABM functionality is designed to increase account relevance, align email signature marketing activity with account strategies, increase campaign engagement and inspire customers and prospects with compelling content. Sigstr’s ABM functionality is available through its Target plan, which also includes recipient-level reporting and time-based analytics.


Sigstr Names Bryan Wade as Chief Executive Officer
Mar 7 17
Sigstr announced former Salesforce Marketing Cloud chief product officer Bryan Wade is joining Sigstr as chief executive officer. Sigstr’s founder Dan Hanrahan will remain with the company as President and shift his focus to leading strategic partnerships and enterprise relationships for the company. With 12 years of marketing SaaS experience, Wade joins Sigstr from Salesforce Marketing Cloud where he served as chief product officer. During his tenure at Salesforce Marketing Cloud, Wade oversaw all product management, product marketing and go-to-market strategy, in addition to shaping product vision and user experience for the Marketing Cloud.


